author: Nerd of the Rings
description:
Today, we take a look at all the fully evil realms of Middle-earth!  From Morgoth's fortresses of the First Age, to Sauron and the Witch-king's dark realms of the Third Age!

00:00-19:09 Angband & Utumno
19:09-28:47 Mordor
28:47-45:39 Angmar
45:39-55:19 The Barrow-downs
55:19-01:04:36 Minas Morgul
01:04:36-01:15:28 Dol Guldur
